{"tid":1642371,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果以後都無6月9日咁大影響力既遊行，香港會輸","createTime":"2019-10-09T16:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T19:06:15.000Z","uid":28105,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6113e0e9e1ab8861970b5c06d3ce5dcd26adcdd9","tid":1642371,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"由六月開始，雖然我唔係勇武，同唔係企係最前線，但一直有遊行活動都會出嚟支持，希望多一個人出嚟表達訴求都好，<br />\n<br />\n但由六月去到而家，開始越來越少人出嚟，<br />\n啲活動亦行動得好散，每日都有唔同嘅活動，冇一個好明確同大型既行動去比和理非一齊去表達訴求嘅。就算有都比之前嘅宣傳同埋號召力低好多，出嚟嘅人數都唔夠。<br />\n<br />\n令藍絲同林鄭有藉口講我哋越來越少人支持，老屈我哋民意逆轉。所我哋一定要再搞一次推動全香港人出嚟，比國際知道我哋香港人大部份嘅訴求，要用人群嘅力量發揮影響力推動到國際。"},{"pid":"8e46657e37bb51d2cd802ff815dacc5dd479b018","tid":1642371,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"f642111987ab41ff3d659b419546091846c6ec32","tid":1642371,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"674ee708624a5f8f229cea34543dae531b336e19","tid":1642371,"uid":323797,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"唔想再黎大圍捕"},{"pid":"77d6ad20ab4b19bb29f5bd26c0af1e58b874867b","tid":1642371,"uid":55955,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民意已經好清晰，唔駛再搞大遊行<br />\n風險大，收穫少"},{"pid":"1e9793ba8c060b6e028a437304198e6004cadf6b","tid":1642371,"uid":28105,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"674ee708624a5f8f229cea34543dae531b336e19","tid":1642371,"uid":323797,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"唔想再黎大圍捕"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"人多同和理非主場嘅時候，唔到佢話拉就拉，如果咁都拉，就令佢比國際譴責"},{"pid":"c3e4cdcfa15a69488f9dd39a3398866131a778b5","tid":1642371,"uid":56023,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"成日輸輸輸<br />\n場紙唔批<br />\n去又去唔到<br />\n走又走唔到<br />\n點樣大遊行呀"},{"pid":"74a12341dcaea93b39a767ad0e419959a4951a6c","tid":1642371,"uid":28105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d6ad20ab4b19bb29f5bd26c0af1e58b874867b","tid":1642371,"uid":55955,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民意已經好清晰，唔駛再搞大遊行<br />\n風險大，收穫少"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"依家就係好多中立或者冇意見嘅人就係覺得開始越來越少人行出嚟表達訴求，開始覺得破壞香港嘅只係一小撮人。"},{"pid":"d950a78b1344049ef488442a4cff420edab755e5","tid":1642371,"uid":34075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e9793ba8c060b6e028a437304198e6004cadf6b","tid":1642371,"uid":28105,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"674ee708624a5f8f229cea34543dae531b336e19","tid":1642371,"uid":323797,"like":4,"dislike":1,"sco